oping you don't get caught by the governing body if you want.The drivers have permanent and temporary traits which change throughout the season. They can develop rivals, get injured, have affairs, get in to fights, find god and even get addicted to video games to name a few.Manage cash flow with sponsors and wages ensuring you can afford to make a competive car for the next year and that you can develop your insanely expensive HQ.At this time I have absolutely nothing bad to say about this game, apart from the scary amount of time I have spent on it in such a short time.Kudos Sega & Playsport, take a bow.Freerider-Dave"
